survival said schabort who claims about 1000 members and many 
more sypathizers 
although no white extremist organizations had been banned the 
government has declared 23 antiapartheid groups illegal and 
detained or restricted hundreds of black activists this year alone 
rightwing white groups have increased in both numbers and 
prominence in recent years as the national party government 
implemented gradual race reforms and proposed limited powersharing 
with blacks 
south africas 26 million blacks have no voice in national 
affairs and the official apartheid policy of race discrimination 
preserves power and privilege for the 5 million whites 
