the golden arm for 25000 a record reprint price at the time he 
also acquired the winds of war and war and remembrance by 
herman wouk 
after pocket books acquired rights to harold robbins it 
established trident press in 1961 to publish his novels in hard 
cover alexander became president of trident as well as editor of a 
number of robbins books including the carpetbaggers 
alexander died wednesday at mount sinai hospital he is survived 
by a son thomas p alexander of manhattan 
